"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_basics\" href=\"UTD.htm?35/25/36242?source=see_link\">",
"      Patient information: Vasectomy (The Basics)",
"     </a>",
"    </p>",
"    <p class=\"headingAnchor2\" id=\"H15696441\">",
"     <span class=\"h3\">",
"      Beyond the Basics",
"     </span>",
