"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_patient\" href=\"UTD.htm?29/2/29730?source=see_link\">",
"      Patient information: Vasectomy (Beyond the Basics)",
"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_patient\" href=\"UTD.htm?37/43/38578?source=see_link\">",
